---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="research — AIIT-THRESHOLD" description="A map, not a menu. Structured descent into the research that moves the framework.">
  <section id="research-hub" class="rh">
    <div class="container narrow rh-inner">
      <div class="rh-head">
        <h1 class="rh-title">research</h1>
        <p class="rh-sub">not everything is explained.<br>some of it is measured.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="rh-framing">
        these are not topics.<br>
        they are pressure points.
      </p>
      <p class="rh-framing rh-framing-soft">
        each one is a system under observation.
      </p>

      <div class="rh-group">
        <div class="rh-group-title">Research</div>
        <div class="rh-grid">
          <a href="/cancer" class="rh-tile">
            <span class="rh-name">Cancer</span>
            <span class="rh-line">pattern extraction in biological collapse</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/weather" class="rh-tile">
            <span class="rh-name">Weather</span>
            <span class="rh-line">coherence signals in atmospheric systems</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/validation" class="rh-tile">
            <span class="rh-name">Validation</span>
            <span class="rh-line">measured performance and failure modes</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/mind" class="rh-tile">
            <span class="rh-name">Mind</span>
            <span class="rh-line">cognition as signal, not abstraction</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/quantum" class="rh-tile">
            <span class="rh-name">Quantum</span>
            <span class="rh-line">field behavior under observation pressure</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/letters" class="rh-tile">
            <span class="rh-name">Letters</span>
            <span class="rh-line">direct communication, unfiltered</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rh-group">
        <div class="rh-group-title">Impact</div>
        <div class="rh-grid">
          <a href="/save-lives" class="rh-tile">
            <span class="rh-name">Save Lives</span>
            <span class="rh-line">real-world intervention pathways</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/drugs" class="rh-tile">
            <span class="rh-name">Low-Cost Drugs</span>
            <span class="rh-line">access over complexity</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/food-dye" class="rh-tile">
            <span class="rh-name">Food Dye</span>
            <span class="rh-line">signal vs ingestion risk</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="rh-closing">
        you don't need all of it.<br>
        just follow the one that holds.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  #research-hub {
    padding: 120px 0 140px;
    min-height: 0;
  }
  .rh-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  .rh-head {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .rh-title {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4em, 6vw, 4em);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .rh-sub {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.82em;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: #888;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .rh-framing {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.25em;
    color: #eaeaea;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .rh-framing-soft {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 1em;
    margin-top: -24px;
  }
  .rh-group {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .rh-group-title {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72em;
    letter-spacing: 5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #666;
    padding-left: 2px;
  }
  .rh-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .rh-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  }
  .rh-tile {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 20px 20px 22px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.15);
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .rh-tile:hover {
    border-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.42);
    background: rgba(212,175,55,0.04);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .rh-name {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.08em;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #eaeaea;
    letter-spacing: 0.2px;
  }
  .rh-line {
    font-size: 0.86em;
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.5;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }
  .rh-closing {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.05em;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 8px 0 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    #research-hub { padding: 80px 0 100px; }
    .rh-inner { gap: 32px; padding: 0 16px; }
    .rh-framing { font-size: 1.1em; }
    .rh-framing-soft { margin-top: -18px; }
  }
</style>
